summary: An Ordinance approving the assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 1346, for the improvement of Third Avenue North, in the City of Seattle, from Garfield Street to Galer Street, by constructing therein a sewer of proper dimensions and material, together with all necessary wyes, etc., under Ordinance No. 14994 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against each parcel and lot of land and part thereof shown in said roll, and providing for the collection thereof.
